 It's 5000km.
 From the beginning, high consumption and low power, making 8km/l on asphalt and not going from 110 to 120km.
 Yesterday it had a gearshift failure and was towed to Fiat Belle in Colatina-ES.
 Technical opinion: I will have to change the clutch system in an amount of R$ 2,700.00.
 They claimed not to be able to invoke the warranty because the car was misused , as it was used on a dirt road , and it is stated in the manual that this type of road is an extreme risk to the vehicle .
 A car with 5,000km, purchased in March/21!!!!
 Disappointment with @fiatbr, terrible after sales, false advertising!
 Don't buy this car, don't take unnecessary risks!!
 Bad acquisition!
 now I will judicialize
